itunes:title: Talking Taylor: 1989 feat. Christina
title: Talking Taylor: 1989 feat. Christina
description: We're back at it with Jessi's BFF Christina and the rest of the crew to discuss Taylor's ultra-famous 1989 album and the songs that changed our lives, We're a little older and a bit wiser but that doesn't stop us from turning into blubbering disasters any time our favorite Taylor Tune gets played!
